723498f.title: Manhattan: Terrace View Avenue - Teunissen Place
723498f.text:
Terrace View Ave., (foreground) west side, at Teunissen Place
(automobile thereon) and viewing northwestward across the valley housing
the New York Central Railroad Freight Yards,to Spuytin Duyvil Hill; a
portion of the Bronx.
October 26, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
